cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.AI 

The paper discusses clustering methods and their evaluation criteria, which are commonly studied in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also proposes objective criteria for evaluating clustering methods, which is a topic of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
